			img(class="front-main-image img-responsive" src='/images/mes-triptych1200.jpg')
		p.front-textbox I'm a software developer and writer from New York City. I've had an incredible 25+ year career at the intersection of arts, culture and technology. Here are some things people tell me I'm good at.

