		.front-feature.col-xs-12.hidden-sm.hidden-md.hidden-lg.hidden-xl
			.col-xs-12.front-feature-words
				.pull-left.front-feature-words-inner
					| <b>Advanced Full Stack Web Development</b> for clients such as <a href="/projects/project/powerbar">PowerBar</a> (Drupal), <a href="/projects/project/center-for-disease-control">Center for Disease Control</a> (Drupal, Solr) and <a href="/projects/project/wellformativecom">Wellformative</a> (Drupal, Drupal Commerce). I'm currently obsessed with Node.js, Angular.js and the MEAN stack, which I believe points the way to the future of web development. I have specialized in content publishing for a long time: my past projects include <a href="/projects/project/words-without-borders">Words Without Borders</a> and (going way back) <a href="/projects/project/pathfinder">Time Warner's Pathfinder</a>, where I learned my craft.
