				.pull-left.front-feature-words-inner
					| I love to see projects I work on succeed, and have often delved deep into <b>Social Media Strategy</a> to help my clients. I launched <a href="/projects/project/foreign-policy">Foreign Policy</a>  magazine's Twitter presence, and helped the Department of Labor-funded project <a href="/projects/project/vcn">Virtual Career Network</a> come up with a UX strategy that attracts audiences. I did early work in this area for <a href="/projects/project/ivillage">iVillage</a>, where I collaborated with the community team on a member profile redesign that brought in millions of pageviews a month and demonstrated the considerable power of organic social marketing.
