				.front-feature-pic-inner
					<img class="img-responsive" src="/images/foreignpolicy600.jpg" />

		// block 4 narrow
		.front-feature.col-xs-12.hidden-sm.hidden-md.hidden-lg.hidden-xl
			.col-xs-12.front-feature-words
				.pull-right.front-feature-words-inner
					| Let's be honest: clients and companies hire me for my tech skills. But I also have a good eye for <b>Art Design</b>, and am proudest of projects on which I've had complete ownership of the visual experience and got to play with Photoshop as well as Linux. I favor Bootstrap for responsive design, enjoy working with advanced LESS and CSS, and always try to stay on top of the ever-changing field of UX. You can get an idea of my web design aesthetic by checking out <a href="/projects/project/law-firm-of-laurence-p-greenberg">The Law Firm of Laurence P. Greenberg</a>, <a href="/projects/project/the-practical-handbook-of-group-counseling">Practical Handbook of Group Counseling</a> and <a href="/projects/project/eli-stein-cartoons">Eli Stein Cartoons</a>.
