				.pull-right.front-feature-words-inner
					| Last but not least: what I'm really all about is <b>Music, Literature & Art</b>. I was the sole coder for <a href="/projects/project/bob-dylan">Bob Dylan's</a> first website back in 1996, and relaunched his website in 2001. I also built an innovative official website for <a href="/projects/project/pearl-jam">Pearl Jam</a> in 2006. The most enduring project of my life (other than parenthood) has been my own literary blog, <a href="/projects/project/literary-kicks">Literary Kicks</a>, which has been online (and morphing and changing with the times) since the summer of 1994.
